snippet.title: Please Don't Hate Christmas | Official Trailer
snippet.description:
You haven't celebrated Christmas for years. This year, you decided to return to your hometown, Snowflake Island, where you rekindle your relationship with an old childhood friend, Albert. However, nothing is as good as it seems.

Full game available for free now: https://rice-love-coffee.itch.io/please-dont-hate-christmas

Full Voice Cast:

Mother -------------------------------------------------- Monique Ranieri (Corpse Party)
